{"tid":1855491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[加速主義]捉到其中一隻中共痛腳","createTime":"2020-02-01T06:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T06:19:20.000Z","uid":327701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8686bae9c361faab8e8d3762e98a5af63640d174","tid":1855491,"uid":327701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AlZ-76CUT3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAlZ-76CUT3s&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=c7f8cf95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AlZ-76CUT3s</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完喱騷最新個CEO會客室 沈旭暉講左樣好重要嘅野：<br />\n<br />\n打國際線 要外國人知道事必關已 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單啲 就係要燒埋人地嗰疊度</span><br />\n<br />\n所以今次個武漢肺炎 其實係個好靚嘅助攻<br />\n<br />\n第一 疫情發展到全球性 係人都怕左芝麻仁 <br />\n而宜家佢地遍佈全世界玩滲透 <br />\n咁我地咪借力打力囉 <br />\n話俾外國人知佢地「未必冇病毒係身」㗎喎 <br />\n咁即係外國人身邊越多芝麻仁 就越危險 <br />\n挽個手當左香港人係芝麻仁   <br />\n發生外資暫緩入資香港之類嘅事 <br />\n咁仲一舉兩得添 <br />\n攬炒之日就越嚟越近啦<br />\n<br />\n將芝麻仁可能有病呢個慨念種落佢地個潛意識度 <br />\n等佢地對芝麻仁開始防範啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 宜家咁多made in china嘅貨等緊出口 <br />\n你又點知啲貨有冇病毒係上面？<br />\n你肯唔肯定整嗰個人冇病毒？<br />\n一個唔覺意打左個乞痴落去件貨度 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻病毒好似話係空氣都生存都一排嘅<br />\n運到過去外國應該乜事都冇啦 你話呀？<br />\n唔怕一萬 至怕萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇成本嘅事大家唔怕做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed682250eeb0bc7168e673c414ab26fdde2cd17","tid":1855491,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊幫幫醫護做勢</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bT0epp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bT0epp.jpg&h=f541a77c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}